{
  "stem": "21786.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now we all-- I simply was told I should find people who know something about washing laundry and washing simply clothes, for we-- we-- went to a [INAUDIBLE] laundry, a big laundry.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we landed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have been-- the first time I remember we had been, there were 70.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The over-specialist in laundry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm sure that nobody has seen a washing machine in his life, or was seen it, but wasn't close.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were-- this was industrial laundry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they were machines which were as big as this wall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, five, six meters long, where you had to come on a small track-- rail track and tip the content of the tracks into the thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then it goes full and distribute it. it-- you close it automatically.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was, I mean, all kinds of solution coming through, and it was-- and then there were huge centrifuges where you had to transfer it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And luckily, when we had just came there, so one of the centrifuges got stuck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And one of the guys was an engineer, so he literally crawled into the-- I don't know what he did-- but it was successful in making it work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that clinched, simply, our knowledge and we were in the laundry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were six German civilian women there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And now the guy who came with us was the chief commanding [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] kind of a Sergeant Major, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE] Bleser-- B-L-E-S-E-R.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We called him the whip, for that was his specialty was to whip people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was quite abrupt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was from the main camp and he was accustomed to give a speech full of threat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So where we were standing, we were prepared for it already.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
